experiences: Worked on  Python, FASTapi, Flask, API, JSON, React

About the project - The MDM data migration project integrates Dun & Bradstreet (D&B) data, enhancing master data management. It includes Identity Resolution and Enrich Call modules for deduplication and data enrichment. The user-friendly UI, built with Flask and FastAPI, ensures secure token-based authentication. The project promotes seamless data exchange, and future enhancements focus on optimizing time efficiency. Additionally, .dat file integration expands the scope of master data enrichment.
